software are free game most of the time. Do you think it would be possible to negotiate 2
new products here so I don't lose this when someone switches. One product would be the
gateway that I could discount as low as possible and then another product for support that
I could mark up slightly.
Thanks Chad

Yesterday

No. We have an enterprise team to pursue those
opportunities.

8:54 PM

Can I ask why?

8:55 PM

Because you make a lot of money on software
maintenance and support and we are in the
payments business for the recurring rev, not the
dealers
This is why we have a VAR program, a referral
program and an enterprise team.
